00:24:14,993 --> 00:24:16,993
Although quite thin,

398
00:24:16,993 --> 00:24:20,293
the string that is drawn taut finally connects to them.

399
00:24:20,293 --> 00:24:21,993
We must be extremely careful

400
00:24:21,993 --> 00:24:23,893
and keep on the look-out

401
00:24:23,893 --> 00:24:25,993
that this string is not severed.

